    id: "en-tox-033", stem: "An emergency nurse is caring for a 70-year-old male with new-onset seizures. His medication list includes isoniazid for latent TB treatment started 2 months ago. Labs show a lactic acidosis with pH 7.15. Which antidote should be administered for isoniazid-induced seizures?",
