    id: "en-tox-036", stem: "A 20-year-old college student presents to the ED after intentionally inhaling a computer duster product (difluoroethane). He collapsed immediately after inhaling and bystanders called 911. In the ED, he develops ventricular fibrillation. What is the primary mechanism of sudden death from inhalant abuse?",
